          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". Additionally, access points on the doors allow squad members to mount automatic weapons for some run-and-gun type moves. For the purpose of the show, it was reported GM Defense mounted up some M240s on the side of the ISV 5 Heavy Gun Carrier to demonstrate its capabilities.",
